1. Hoćeš* li da ideš sa mnom u bioskop? (Do you want* to go to the movies with me?)
2. Ja ne znam šta *hoćeš od mene. (I don't know what you want* from me.)
3. *Hoćeš li* mi pomoći da nosim ove kofere? (Will you help me carry these suitcases?)
4. Ne razumem šta mi *hoćeš reći. (I don't understand what you're trying to tell me.)
5. On neće da mi kaže šta *hoće* od mene. (He doesn't want to tell me what he wants* from me.)
6. *Hoćeš li* da ti ispričam vic? (Do you want me to tell you a joke?)
7. Moramo da odlučimo šta *hoćemo* da uradimo. (We need to decide what we want* to do.)
8. *Hoćeš li* da se vidimo posle posla? (Do you want to meet up after work?)
9. Ona *hoće* da ode u šoping. (She wants* to go shopping.)
10. *Hoćeš li* mi pozajmiti novac? (Will you lend me some money?)